Class HandlerPriorityRuleImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • MinimalEObjectImpl.Container
      • org.eclipse.scada.configuration.world.impl.HandlerPriorityRuleImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HandlerPriorityRule

    public class HandlerPriorityRuleImpl
extends MinimalEObjectImpl.Container
implements HandlerPriorityRule
    An implementation of the model object 'Handler Priority Rule'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Order
    • Factory Id
    • Configuration Filter
    • Priority
    • Description
